    <title>
      Scaling Mixture-of-Experts with Curriculum Learning for
      Multi-Agent Reasoning
    </title>
    <summary>
      We, at OpenAI, propose a novel approach to scaling MoE models for
      multi-agent reasoning tasks using curriculum learning. Our method
      combines RLHF and chain-of-thought fine-tuning to improve emergent
      tool use behaviors in long-horizon agentic workflows.
    </summary>
